dc_title_s: Insurance maps of Trenton, New Jersey, volume 1, sheet 52
dc_description_s: Includes index key map, "New index, February, 1955" for streets, and legend. Includes record of insertion and correction done from 1957-1960. Foot note: "This record supersedes similar record on individual sheets of this map". The updates were paste on the original sheet. "Copyright 1955". These maps were digitized from a copy held by the Trenton Free Public Library, housed in the Trentoniana Collection. Call number: 912.9 INSU
